snippet.title: Rappler
snippet.description:
Rappler is a Manila-based online news platform – a social news network.
In this channel you will find the latest news on politics, technology, business, and sports.
Also here are the daily Rappler Newscast, and weekly sit-down interviews with key personalities.
You will also find here Rappler's latest documentaries, commentaries, entertainment features, special coverages and animation.
